UID:rrmZ8362udoNx66dEnYpS
SUMMARY:Socialist Soccer! 2pm - 4pm
DTSTAMP:20260325T060838Z
DTSTART:20260329T140000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come play soccer with fellow socialists! This is a fun\\\, enjo
	yable way to get outdoors\\\, exercise\\\, and meet friendly socialists as
	 well as non-socialist soccer enthusiasts! \\nAll genders and skill levels
	 are welcome! Safety is our top priority. To participate you must abide by
	 our norms and agreements to avoid injuries and help us take care of one a
	nother. \\nJoin us at Brighton Playfield in South Seattle. Map: goo.gl/map
	s/c74cytjrRB1vpT7h7\\nWe almost always play on the most southern edge of t
	he field. \\nWe confirm if we have enough players each Sunday on a sociali
	st soccer Signal chat. To be added\\\, download the Signal app\\\, and ema
	il your phone number to tdupuis42@gmail.com with a request to be added. \\
	nThe game is usually at 10 AM\\\, but that may change\\\, so make sure you
	 are on the Socialist Soccer signal chat!\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org/event/
	socialist-soccer-2pm-4pm/2026-03-29/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
URL:https://seattledsa.org/event/socialist-soccer-2pm-4pm/2026-03-29/
